KUSHONE abantu abathathu kwalimala abalinganiselwa ngaphezulu kuka-200 kushayisana izitimela esiteshini iMountain View ePretoria ngoLwesibili ekuseni. Abezimo eziphuthumayo bathi baningi abanye abasezimeni ezibucayi kodwa ibingakaqinisekiswa imibiko yokuthi sesinyukile isibalo sabadlulile kule ngozi. “Ngokwemibiko evela endaweni yesigameko kusadlule abantu ababili okudingeke ukuthi baphuthunyiswe esibhedlela ngendiza,” kusho okhulumela iNetcare 911 ephawula ngaphambi kokuthi kuqinisekiswe ukushona kowesithathu. “Balinganiselwa ku-200 abanye abalimalile kodwa  bathole imihuzuko kuphela. Okwamanje asinalo ulwazi ngokuholele kule ngozi kodwa amaphoyisa akhona endaweni yesigameko.”     Pretoria - #TrainCrash #MetroRail Multiple injuries at Mountain View station pic.twitter.com/kNUJpjuUGS To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
